paragraph: Mike Schuppan is an American producer, mixing engineer and recording engineer.  He is known for his work with Paramore, M83, Jimmy Eat World and others. He has been the long time engineer for Justin Meldal-Johnsen and served as his bass tech while touring with  Nine Inch Nails and Beck. Mike has a private studio in Hollywood, California.
2014 Young The Giant - Mind Over Matter
2015 Yacht - I Thought The Future Would Be Cooler
2017 Wolf Alice - Visions Of A Life
2017 Foster The People - Sacred Hearts Club
2018 Jimmy Eat World - Love Never/Half Heart
